description.3: One of the Hulk's oldest and most storied rivalries comes bubbling back to the surface! On his way to the Savage Land, Hulk doesn't realize that he is being tracked...by none other than Wolverine! Get ready for a grudge match for the ages!
description.7: After tasting victory, the X-Men head straight into another disaster. Meanwhile, someone or something has been tailing Joseph...
description.13: The fake Prowler is out on the streets and seeking revenge. Spider-Man and the false Prowler battle it out, but Spidey suffers from the repercussions of Morbius' bite.
description.15: Felicia Hardy is Black Cat! A renowned cat burglar and stealth agent, Black Cat's rise as one of Spidey's favorite foes has had unexpected twists and turns along the way. Learn them here!
description.16: The'Empire'is dying, perhaps in its final throes. But like a dog near death, that's when it is most dangerous, when it will lash out with nothing to lose. The ruthless warlord'Grand Admiral'Thrawn'may have found just the firepower needed to take a bite out of the'New Republic: Some two hundred Dreadnaught'heavy cruisers, lost to'hyperspace'in the days of the'Old Republic.'Luke,'Leia,'Han, and'Chewbacca'may be up against more than they bargained for, but it's not the first time the odds have been stacked against them!
description.17: Han and Chewie take a well-deserved break on the planet of Rudrig! But before the duo can settle into a life of leisure, a "friend" from Han's past resurfaces with an unusual offer. Who is the Queen of Ranroon? What is the legend that surrounds her?
description.22: Only one thing can possibly break the Hulk's iron grip on Hulk Island...the Incredible Hulk! But why has this Hulk from the future approached the Hulk of today? Is he a friend or foe?
description.24: It should have been a simple mission for the men and women of Rogue Squadron-an easy search-and-rescue for a group of Bothan castaways forced down on Malrev IV. But when they got to the backwater planet, the Rogues found themselves first attacked by the Irrukiine, a doglike aboriginal race, and then by the Bothans themselves. There's some strange kind of hoodoo going down on Malrev 4-this planet promotes madness and deceit, and not even the Rogues are immune!
description.26: An army of assassins are turning NYC into a bloodbath, and there's only one way our anti-hero can survive! That's right, Elektra's back to her old wicked ways. Meanwhile, the ancient being known only as the Architect offers Konrad Weiss what he's always wanted - but to get it, Konrad will have to sell out Elektra.
description.32: The X-Men battle the Phalanx in the Shi'Ar royal palace!
description.37: A memorial to those killed by Onslaught is interrupted by the Mad Thinker! Will the Thunderbolts stop him from kidnapping Franklin Richards?
description.39: Risque is on the run after drugging and kidnapping Warpath! Will blending in at the Wackyworld theme park be enough to keep X-Force from the answers they need to find their friend?
description.42: From beloved child, to pickpocketing street urchin, to revered goddess, learn the incredible history of the X-Men's Storm!
description.44: ELECTRO-CUTED! Stuck in the middle of Dragonfly vs. Robertson, Electro vs. Dragonfly, Spider-Man tries to put an end to it all but falls short when Robertson lets Dragonfly and the Believers escape.
description.48: Someone has stolen Hobie's "Prowler" costume and all his gadgets. It's up to Spider-Man to find the fake Prowler, but he's not the only one looking for him…
description.50: Han Solo and Chewbacca accept a rogue mission from an unidentified employer. Who Is Fiolla? And what is her personal mission against the Empire?
description.56: Malrev IV is an uncivilized planet in a pretty, but otherwise useless, corner of the galaxy. Inhabited by vicious, unthinking brutes, it's like a living museum of pre-evolution. You wouldn't bother going there unless you had a death wish... or you were a member of Rogue Squadron and you were trying to rescue a downed cruise liner.
description.57: The stunning conclusion to the four-issue event that captures the first Star Wars motion picture! Your favorite aspects of the Star Wars universe, captured in one exciting comic!
description.59: Blood, death, revenge and madness - who says modern dance is dull? While Elektra opens her off-Broadway show, the being known as Architect, stung by Elektra's refusal to assassinate him, brings the curtain up on his own even more savage performance!
description.61: In an action packed issue Madame Qwa continues training the new Dragonfly, Fortunato and Rose team up against Tarantula and we meet the "all-new, supremely powerful and super charged" Electro. FEAR THE RETURN OF ELECTRO!
description.65: Welcome to HULK ISLAND! There are only two laws...1: Leave the Hulk alone, and you live. And 2: No one leaves Hulk Island! How will the government respond to the Hulk taking five thousand people hostage!?
description.69: The Phalanx have infiltrated the X-Men by assuming the identities of several members. To save themselves, the team must allow their ship to be destroyed. Stranded in space, the  X-Men must hatch a daring plan to survive.
description.71: The X-Men take on Shinobi Shaw!
description.74: A secretive new super-team has emerged in a world sorely missing its heroes. Will they be able to replace Earth's Mightiest Heroes, or will supervillains run rampant?
description.75: The Hulk and The Bird have made their way to the Savage Land just in time for the dams to burst and flood!
description.79: From circus freak to X-Man! Learn the origin of Nightcrawler, teleporting mutant swashbuckler, in this tragic tale of family strife and redemption!
description.86: It's up to Han Solo and Chewbacca to fly the Millenium Falcon into safe territory. But without an official Waiver from the Empire, what lengths will Han go to to keep the Falcon flying?
description.91: Collects Star Wars: Heir to the Empire (1995) #1-6.  The tyranny has ended. But what will take its place? It is now five years after Return of the Jedi. Leia and Han are married and have shouldered heavy burdens in the government of the New Republic. And Luke Skywalker is the first in a hoped-for new line of Jedi Knights.  But thousands of light-years away, the last of the Emperor's warlords, Grand Admiral Thrawn, has taken command of the remains of the Imperial fleet. Thrawn has made two vital discoveries that could destroy the Rebel Alliance's New Republic. The tale that emerges is a towering epic of action, invention, mystery, and a spectacle of galactic scale—in short, a story that is worthy of the name Star Wars.
description.92: The adaptation of the first Star Wars motion picture continues!'Luke Skywalker continues his meteoric rise in becoming a Jedi.
description.94: Doctor Strange guest-stars! After taking in Nina, Elektra seeks the help of the Sorcerer Supreme to eliminate the Architect.
description.99: Caught in a military trap, the Hulk has no choice but to escape to a nearby island! But this time, he's not just running away. Hulk cuts the island off from civilization, digs in his heels, and dares the military to try and take...HULK ISLAND!

1.text: The second issue of Waid and Kubert's Ka-Zar reinvention!

2.text: Meggan and Captain Britain may have hit their breaking points against the Dragons of the Crimson Dawn.

6.text: Get ready for the HEROES REBORN debut of The Inhumans!

9.text: The team is beaten by Bastion, and all of Professor Xavier’s secrets threaten to be exposed.

11.text: The aftermath of the Clay Surfer’s attack transports Surfer and Alicia to 1947! Surfer has his emotions back, but will that help him return to the present?

12.text: The Masters of Evil are here...but weren't they already?! Will the Thunderbolts be able to fight their former allies?

14.text: Venom…Federal Agent? It’s true! The Lethal Protector takes on a new assignment, this time working for the United States to take down the nation’s most loathsome and abominable threats.

18.text: Captain America doesn't want to be a pawn of S.H.I.E.L.D. any longer! He's striking out on his own and no one can stop him now, not even the President of the good ol' U, S, and A!

20.text: At the mercy of Bastion, could Jubilee really be the sole survivor of the X-Men?

21.text: Deadpool sets out to kill...Dr. Killebrew? Plus, things heat up with Siryn!

23.text: The original five X-Men join Spidey to incapacitate a new to the scene mutant!

25.text: Inferno plummets the entire city into madness. Piper makes amends with his wife.

26.text: An army of assassins are turning NYC into a bloodbath, and there's only one way our anti-hero can survive! That's right, Elektra's back to her old wicked ways. Meanwhile, the ancient being known only as the Architect offers Konrad Weiss what he's always wanted - but to get it, Konrad will have to sell out Elektra.

27.text: Daredevil fights Insomnia and saves Karen from a sleepless eternity!

28.text: Will Spiral become the unexpected ally that Excalibur needs?

31.text: Ben Grimm may be recuperating in the hospital, but The Fantastic Four are still on the job! Next stop: The Negative Zone! Featuring The X-Men!

34.text: What will the X-Men do with the cure for the Legacy Virus?

36.text: Silver Surfer’s Puppet Master doppelganger is on the loose! Spider-Man and Daredevil guest-star to put the kibosh on the Clay Surfer…but the damage to New York City is done! Plus, the original Surfer reverts back to Norrin Radd!

38.text: An explosion rocks Stark International and someone close to Tony Stark is killed! Who is the mysterious perpetrator in a suit of cybernetic armor?

40.text: Aurora might need rescuing from Department H…but that's the last thing on Nate's mind when Dark Beast reveals he is a member of The Brotherhood!

43.text: Relive the second generation of X-Men, fighting villains like the Juggernaut and Magneto, and discover the human within the hero, and the truth behind the legend.

47.text: Ka-Zar by Mark Waid and Andy Kubert!

49.text: Venom, Spider-Man and Daredevil battle Carnage…in the courtroom! Once everything “comes to order”, Venom is taken into custody by a secret agent!

51.text: Deadpool is dying!Â  But what will get him first...his unexplained ailment or the Incredible Hulk?Â  (We're betting on the latter.)

52.text: The Vulture’s murderous spree can only be quelled by the Friendly Neighborhood wall-crawler!

54.text: When her back is put against the wall, Jubilee becomes unleashed!  But who will pay the price?

55.text: Cable has been transported aboard the S.H.I.E.L.D. helicarrier where Cap and Bucky are staving off a M.O.D.O.K.-led invasion. But Captain America doesn't have the faintest idea who Cable is!

58.text: The Code of Honor cops deal with the fallout from the first Secret Wars. Earth’s Heroes have vanished without a trace. Which means emboldened super villains are left to wreak havoc in the streets!

59.text: Blood, death, revenge and madness - who says modern dance is dull? While Elektra opens her off-Broadway show, the being known as Architect, stung by Elektra's refusal to assassinate him, brings the curtain up on his own even more savage performance!

60.text: Forever locked in struggle to keep his berserker fury in check, Logan is a man without a past on a never-ending journey to uncover the truth about himself. Featuring Sabretooth and Lady Deathstrike.

63.text: Why is Daredevil fighting Karen’s boss?!

64.text: The Dragons of the Crimson Dawn antagonize Excalibur for the fate of Great Britain!

68.text: While Alicia Masters waits for Ben Grimm to show up for their date, The Fantastic Four battles The Super-Skrull! Featuring, The Silver Sufer!

71.text: The X-Men take on Shinobi Shaw!

73.text: Silver Surfer gives Alicia Masters a new way to ‘see’ the world. Seeking a cure for his amnesia and emotional roadblock, Surfer enlists the aid of the Puppet Master to create a new Silver Surfer ‘copy’ with all the memories of its original.

76.text: During Venom’s trial, things take a bad turn when Cletus Kasady, (that’s Carnage to you), takes the stand!

77.text: The final confrontation between Gambit, Anielle and Stoker! Will Gambit and the personified star survive this conflict?

80.text: The resurrection of Carrion! In this double-sized epic, you’ll gain insider knowledge about Spidey’s most macabre menace.

82.text: The damaged gamma core that threatens to destroy the entire Eastern seaboard can only be fixed by Bruce Banner. But Banner is nowhere to be found. There is only The Hulk!

84.text: Following the blowout of his telekinesis, Nate seeks the aid of Moira MacTaggert on Muir Isle to restore his abilities.

88.text: The World Party is about to launch their nuclear weapons-only S.H.I.E.L.D. and Captain American can stop them!

89.text: Deadpool's healing factor has gone kaput.Â  Just how is Black Tom Cassidy involved?Â  Guess he'd better go ask his niece (and Deadpool's crush of the week): Siryn of X-Force!

90.text: Spider-Man takes on Doc Ock! And Aunt May is none the wiser!

93.text: Jeff Piper celebrates a personal milestone, but suffers a professional setback. Thanks to…The Punisher!

94.text: Doctor Strange guest-stars! After taking in Nina, Elektra seeks the help of the Sorcerer Supreme to eliminate the Architect.

95.text: Gambit and Anielle flee the country as the evil Stoker chases them down!

97.text: Matt obsesses over Black Widow and Daredevil rescues Rosalind!

98.text: Can Nightcrawler lead Excalibur towards a new dawn?
